<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749302' id='t-749302'>She was a 10-year-old girl from Surrey, England</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751985' id='t-751985'>on vacation with her parents a few years ago in Phuket, Thailand.</span>
